  ('heelevel3-acfc4025-moex-00273', 'heelevel3-acfc4025', 'heelevel3-acfc4025-moex-110-bd2490ec', 'sub-heelevel3-acfc4025-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有兩個隨機變數X與Y，我們以P (x,y)=Prob(X=x,Y=y)來代表其合併機率函數（jointprobability XY function），且其值如下所示：P (1,1)=0.07、P (1,2)=0.09、P (1,3)=0.12、P (2,1)=0.25、 XY XY XY XY P (2,2)=0.07、P (2,3)=0.18、P (3,1)=0.06、P (3,2)=0.07、P (3,3)=0.09。請計算下列條件 XY XY XY XY XY 機率之值：Prob(Y=3X=2)=？', '["0.25", "0.36", "0.60", "0.84"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8af2c276482d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "375d475f31ab", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110090", "c": "377", "s": "1201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "工程數學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
